::Hot Rod::

The Key to Vector Sigma blasts did nothing to Hot Rod. It was a good
thing he didn't have a beast mode, or any organic parts. If he did he
would be turning in to pure metal now. But his body was more a scaled
down Autobot then a Maximal.
"I wish Alpha Trion could see you now. An evil, treacherous fool! I
spent my whole life trying to live up to you, and you become this?! You
turn your back on Alpha Trion, Vector Sigma, the Matrix, and your
Autobot haratige? I despise you!"
Hot Rod launches two missiles at Dark Prime.
